txt.en: You have increased your Rank!  This is achieved by acquiring Glory Points. Each Rank has a title associated with it. Higher Ranks may give you greater rewards.

You have increased your Rank! This is achieved by acquiring Renown/Infamy Points. Each Rank has a title associated with it. Higher Ranks may give you greater rewards.  You can view additional details about your Rank on The War panel, found within Character options.
